msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:3
msgid ""
"This page covers the backend SPARQL query, TypeScript interfaces, and "
"frontend components that implement the DMN validation badge system."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:7
msgid "Backend — SPARQL query"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:9
msgid ""
"Validation metadata is fetched alongside DMN data in `findAllDmns` using "
"`OPTIONAL` blocks that do not break when governance data is absent:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:11
msgid ""
"PREFIX ronl: <https://regels.overheid.nl/ontology#>\n"
"\n"
"SELECT ...\n"
"WHERE {\n"
"  ?dmn a cprmv:DecisionModel ;\n"
"       dct:identifier ?identifier ;\n"
"       dct:title ?title .\n"
"\n"
"  # Governance metadata (all optional)\n"
"  OPTIONAL { ?dmn ronl:validationStatus ?validationStatus }\n"
"  OPTIONAL {\n"
"    ?dmn ronl:validatedBy ?validatedBy .\n"
"    OPTIONAL { ?validatedBy skos:prefLabel ?validatedByName . }\n"
"  }\n"
"  OPTIONAL { ?dmn ronl:validatedAt ?validatedAt }\n"
"  OPTIONAL { ?dmn ronl:validationNote ?validationNote }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:31
msgid ""
"The `validatedByName` is resolved via `skos:prefLabel` on the organisation "
"URI (`ronl:validatedBy` points to a URI, not a literal). If the organisation "
"resource has no `skos:prefLabel`, the badge renders without the organisation "
"name — graceful degradation."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:35
msgid "Backend — TypeScript interface"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:37
msgid ""
"// In sparql.service.ts DmnModel interface\n"
"interface DmnModel {\n"
"  id: string;\n"
"  identifier: string;\n"
"  title: string;\n"
"  // ... core fields ...\n"
"\n"
"  // Governance fields\n"
"  validationStatus?: 'validated' | 'in-review' | 'not-validated';\n"
"  validatedBy?: string;        // Organisation URI\n"
"  validatedByName?: string;    // Resolved skos:prefLabel\n"
"  validatedAt?: string;        // ISO 8601 date string\n"
"  validationNote?: string;\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:56
msgid "Frontend — ValidationBadge component"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:58
msgid ""
"`ValidationBadge.tsx` renders conditionally based on `validationStatus`. No "
"badge renders for `\"not-validated\"` or when `validationStatus` is absent:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:60
msgid ""
"interface ValidationBadgeProps {\n"
"  status: 'validated' | 'in-review' | 'not-validated' | undefined;\n"
"  validatedByName?: string;\n"
"  validatedAt?: string;\n"
"  compact?: boolean;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"const ValidationBadge: React.FC<ValidationBadgeProps> = ({\n"
"  status, validatedByName, validatedAt, compact\n"
"}) => {\n"
"  if (!status || status === 'not-validated') return null;\n"
"\n"
"  const isValidated = status === 'validated';\n"
"\n"
"  return (\n"
"    <span\n"
"      className={`badge ${isValidated ? 'badge-green' : 'badge-amber'}`}\n"
"      title={`${validatedByName ?? ''} ${validatedAt ?? ''}`}\n"
"    >\n"
"      {isValidated ? '✓ Gevalideerd' : '⏱ In Review'}\n"
"    </span>\n"
"  );\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:86
msgid ""
"The `compact` prop reduces the badge to a small indicator for use on Chain "
"Composer cards where space is limited."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:90
msgid "Frontend — integration points"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:92
msgid "`DmnList.tsx` — badge appears on each card in the Available DMNs panel"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cgovernance.md:93
msgid ""
"`ChainComposer.tsx` — badge persists on cards after they are dropped into "
"the chain"
msgstr ""

